Class Supplement

  • java.lang.Object
    • magazine_service.Supplement
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Supplement
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    The Supplement class represents a supplement offered in the magazine service. It contains information about the supplement's name and weekly cost.
